&quot;Ah!  Well, perhaps he'll kill himself!&quot;  With his thoughts resolved, Kelisk quickened his pace to seek a new adventure. <p><center><b>Kelisk Mae'Lokh</b></center><br><center>Chancellor of Skathris Ven'Sho--Patriarch of Cabilis</center><br><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=355953"><i>Inspect Kelisk?</i></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umadrain.showPublicProfile?language=EN>madrain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Kerran Lord</span><br>  Posts: 833<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/7/02 8:26:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=108.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re:What it takes to be A True Hearted Evil Bastard</span><hr size=1> Lashun Novashine takes a cookie and shouts, &quot;Theef thif endleff confwict am seek sowfation in the Temble of Wife!  The gory of Wodcet Nife awaits you!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=108.topic&start=21&stop=34>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=108.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=108.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=108.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.threadControl?topicID=108.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/